│ Avg Latency        │                     12.3ms   │
│ Max Latency        │                    156.2ms   │
│ Active Connections │                          2   │
│ Data Received      │                    4.2 MB    │
│ Data Sent          │                   12.8 MB    │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

